In other words......<br>
<br>
Welcome to EQ, clerics get to DEMAND money for a rezz, Druids and Shamen get paid to SoW(Rangers now), Wizzies and Druids get to TP, Necro's summon Corpses and Enchanters...well Enchanters get into a group to Clarity and speed.<br>
<br>
Now, enchanters get KEI (IMHO VI did bad allowing this to be cast on anyone under at least L50, dont get me wrong, my twinkie mage pays for a hit as soon as the last one wears off...donation only so i pay what I think its worth, bout 50ppa shot for a L31 mage and will prolly pay more as i level up) and EVERYONE starts shouting FOUL !!!!!!<br>
<br>
Well as you posted, you dont NEED KEI to level, if you dont want it then dont pay for it. No One NEEDS a buff or an effect to level, sure it helps, Run faster, Move from Loc to Loc in the blink of an eye, be rezzed and save xp. All things you expect in a group, but also something 99% of folks CHARGE FOR WHEN NOT IN A GROUP !!<br>
<br>
WHY should Enchanters give the one buff they CAN charge for for FREE ??<br>
